OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Rob
OL,7,FSmith has been speaking to the family
OL,8,Fof Megan Hilton whose organs saved the
OL,9,Flives of five strangers.
OL,11,FA teenage girl who aspired to be a
OL,12,Fpaediatric nurse has saved the lives
OL,13,Fof five strangers after signing up to
OL,14,Fthe organ donor register weeks before
OL,15,Fher sudden death.
