OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FMegan Hilton, described as having a
OL,7,F"kind soul" whose "masterplan" was to
OL,8,Fgo to university and care for others,
OL,9,Fsuffered a brain aneurism "completely
OL,10,Fout of the blue" and died in hospital
OL,11,Fsix days later.
OL,13,FA couple of months before her death,
OL,14,Fthe 17-year-old from Bootle, told her
OL,15,Fdad, David Hilton, that she had ticked
OL,16,Fon her driving license application
OL,17,Fthat she wanted to donate her organs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
