OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,F"She donated blood as well, as soon as
OL,7,Fshe turned 17, as soon as she could,"
OL,8,FDavid said. "That was Megan all over.
OL,9,FShe was always thinking of others."
OL,11,FThere are more than 8,000 people on
OL,12,Fthe UK transplant waiting list,
OL,13,Faccording to the latest NHS figures,
OL,14,Fand as many as five people die every
OL,15,Fweek as a result of not finding a
OL,16,Fdonor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
