OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FAll adults in England are now
OL,7,Fconsidered potential organ donors,
OL,8,Funless they choose to opt out, are in
OL,9,Fone of the excluded groups, or under
OL,10,F18 years old.
OL,12,FWhen Megan was dying at Aintree
OL,13,FHospital, her parents spoke to a
OL,14,FSpecialist Nurse in Organ Donation,
OL,15,Fwho talked them through the process of
OL,16,Fdonating their daughter's organs.
OL,18,FDavid, Megan's dad, recalls the moment
OL,19,Fhis daughter told him she'd opted to
OL,20,Fdonate her organs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
