OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,F"When we had to make a decision, we
OL,7,Fknew that's what she wanted," David
OL,8,Fsaid. "It made a really difficult
OL,9,Fsituation much easier for us."
OL,11,F"We're thankful that we did have that
OL,12,Fconversation," David added. "Organ
OL,13,Fdonation is not something people talk
OL,14,Fabout. People know what songs and
OL,15,Fcolours they want at their funeral -
OL,16,Ffor us, this was just as important.
OL,18,F"This is the best send off ever
OL,19,Fbecause we know Megan has helped so
OL,20,Fmany people."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
