OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FMegan wanted to be a paediatric nurse
OL,7,Fand had been researching the
OL,8,Funiversities she wanted to apply for.
OL,10,FDavid said: "She would've been a
OL,11,Ffantastic nurse and she would've cared
OL,12,Ffor people so much. Unfortunately, she
OL,13,Fcouldn't do that, but she has still
OL,14,Fhelped people by giving them that gift
OL,15,Fof life."
OL,17,FThe nurse who worked with Megan's
OL,18,Ffamily through the process says her
OL,19,Fdonation has made a huge difference,
OL,20,Fwith some organ recipients having been
OL,21,Fon the wait list for years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
