OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FCatherine Ellis, Specialist Nurse for
OL,7,FOrgan Donation, said: "If I could talk
OL,8,Fto Megan today I would thank her for
OL,9,Fthe amazing decision to made to join
OL,10,Fthe organ donation register.
OL,12,F"I don't think you can put into words
OL,13,Fhow much of an impact families and
OL,14,Fdonors have. She is a hero."
OL,16,FA fundraiser has been set up in
OL,17,FMegan's name to raise money for Alder
OL,18,FHey, in Liverpool, where Megan aspired
OL,19,Fto work when she trained as a neonatal
OL,20,Fnurse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
