OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FWhat is organ donation?
OL,8,FOrgan donation is a process where an
OL,9,Forgan, like a heart, kidney or liver,
OL,10,For tissue is removed from one person
OL,11,Fand given to another person who needs
OL,12,Fit.
OL,14,FIf someone donates one or more of
OL,15,Ftheir organs, this could help save the
OL,16,Flives of multiple people. Thousands of
OL,17,Flives in the UK are saved each year by
OL,18,Forgan transplants.
OL,20,FHow can I become a donor?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
