OL,3,CThe aspiring nurse who saved five
OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FAnyone can register a decision to
OL,7,Fbecome an organ donor after death,
OL,8,Fthere is no age limit.
OL,10,FThose over the age of 18 in England
OL,11,Fare presumed to be an organ donor when
OL,12,Fthey die, unless they have made a
OL,13,Fdecision that they do not want to be a
OL,14,Fdonor, or they are in a group who are
OL,15,Fnot allowed be donors.
OL,17,FSince 2020, people have to choose to
OL,18,Fopt out. It is hoped this new system
OL,19,Fwill save more lives.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
