OL,4,Clives after sudden death
OL,6,FThose under 18 can join the NHS Organ
OL,7,FDonor Register, although those with
OL,8,Fparental responsibility have the final
OL,9,Fdecision.
OL,11,FThe NHS says it is "quick and easy" to
OL,12,Fregister your decision on the NHS
OL,13,FOrgan Donor Register.
